Mati%20Staniszewski%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02a351e1443b8dc48e41b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222261%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMati%20Staniszewski%20says%20adding%20an%20engineer%20to%20each%20team%20can%20upskill%20it.%3Cp%3EBig%20Event%20Media%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20HumanX%20Conference%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElevenLabs%20CEO%20Mati%20Staniszewski%20said%20he's%20adding%20engineers%20to%20non-technical%20teams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20that%20non-technical%20teams%20around%20the%20company%20are%20already%20building%20tools%20for%20their%20use%20cases.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20has%20a%20micro-team%20structure%20for%20end-to-end%20ownership.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20one%20thing%20you%20need%20before%20you%20can%20vibe%20code%20everything%3A%20An%20engineer%20to%20show%20you%20how.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20talk%20at%20Sequoia%20Capital%20released%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felevenlabs-micro-team-hire-interview-voice-cloning-ai-staniszewski-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElevenLabs%20CEO%20Mati%20Staniszewski%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20he%20is%20adding%20an%20engineer%20to%20every%20non-technical%20team%20inside%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startup-elevenlabs-raising-third-round-this-year-sources-say-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evoice%20AI%20company%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20people%20team%2C%20our%20go-to-market%20team%2C%20our%20legal%20team%20will%20have%20an%20engineer%20in%20that%20team%20that%20helps%20to%20build%20automation%20and%20upskill%2C%20uplevel%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20that%20really%20helps%20because%20everybody%20will%20be%20vibe%20coding%20and%20coding%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaniszewski%2C%20who%20cofounded%20ElevenLabs%20in%202022%2C%20said%20that%20non-t