n%20tourism%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Air%20Canada%20airplane%20at%20Calgary%20International%20Airport%20in%20Calgary%2C%20Alberta%2C%20Canada.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02665cc9dd4cb81cda960e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECanadians%20appear%20to%20be%20making%20far%20fewer%20work%20trips%2C%20new%20cell%20phone%20data%20show.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDonald%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20has%20had%20a%20large%20impact%20on%20Canadian%20tourism.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20analysis%20out%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%20suggests%20that%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20US%20economy%20have%20taken%20a%20major%20hit%20as%20well.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20findings%20underscore%20how%20the%20relationship%20between%20Canada%20and%20the%20US%20is%20under%20strain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economic%20effects%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20disruptive%20approach%20to%20foreign%20policy%20are%20coming%20into%20sharper%20focus%20with%20a%20year's%20worth%20of%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20a%20range%20of%20numbers%20like%20border%20crossings%20and%20hotel%20bookings%20show%20how%20Trump's%20trade%20war%20has%20killed%20off%20a%20large%20segment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanadians-are-still-unhappy-with-trump-hesitant-about-us-travels-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanadian%20tourism%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmappingtariffs.org%2Fcanada-us-visits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto's%20School%20of%20Cities%20now%20shows%20that%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20economy%20have%20taken%20a%20major%20hit%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20cell%20phone%20data%2C%20researchers%20Karen%20Chapple%2C%20Yihoi%20Jung%2C%20and%20Jeff%20Allen%20documented%20an%20average%20year-over-year%20decline%20in%20Canadian%20visits%20to%20US%20cities%20of%20approximately%2042%25.%20That's%20a%20much%20larger%20hit%20than%20the%2025%25%20drop%20previously%20estimated%20based%20on%20border%20crossing%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20top%2020%20cities%20were%20a%20number%20of%20big%20metros%20that%20aren't%20exactly%20known%20as%2C%20you%20know%2C%20big%20tourist%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Chapple%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222098%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20visualization%20of%20the%20drop-off%20of%20Canadian%20tourism%20to%20US%20cities%2C%20based%20on%20cell%20phone%20data%20analysis%20from%20University%20of%20Toronto%20researchers.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0273a8e1443b8dc48e4174%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221216%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20visualization%20of%20the%20drop-off%20of%20Canadian%20tourism%20to%20US%20cities%2C%20based%20on%20cell%20phone%20data%20analysis.%3Cp%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fmappingtariffs.org%2Fcanada-us-visits%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20drop-offs%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20Orlando%20could%20reasonably%20be%20attributed%20to%20less%20tourism%2C%20major%20commercial%20hubs%20like%20New%20York%2C%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20San%20Francisco%2C%20Dallas%2C%20and%20Houston%20also%20saw%20significant%20declines.%20The%20researchers%20attribute%20the%20change%20to%20fewer%20tech%20and%20finance%20employees%20making%20work%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20fly%20to%20San%20Francisco%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Chapple%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20tech%20flight%20to%20San%20Francisco%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20who's%20with%20me%20on%20the%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChapple%20said%20her%20team%20was%20particularly%20surprised%20by%20mid-sized%20cities%20like%20Grand%20Rapids%20and%20Flint%2C%20Michigan%2C%20which%20have%20robust%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F