20Mohanlal%20and%20Nayanthara%2C%20has%20garnered%20significant%20collections%20both%20in%20India%20and%20overseas.%20Actress%20Zarin%20Shihab%20also%20shared%20insights%20into%20her%20role%20and%20the%20filmmaking%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22GitLab%20employees%20are%20the%20latest%20to%20face%20layoffs%20limbo.%20Read%20the%20CEO's%20memo%20about%20restructuring%20'openly.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226158%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22GitLab%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a025ed2ba7ef34b41f3736c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224105%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGitLab's%20CEO%20announced%20plans%20to%20lay%20off%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20employees.%3Cp%3EJaque%20Silva%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGitLab%20stock%20is%20down%20after%20hours%20following%20its%20plans%20to%20lay%20off%20staff%20as%20it%20looks%20to%20meet%20the%20%26quot%3Bagentic%20era.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20planning%20is%20happening%20openly%2C%20including%20a%20voluntary%20separation%20window%2C%26quot%3B%20GitLab's%20CEO%20wrote%20in%20a%20memo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20CEO%20acknowledged%20the%20limbo%20period%20%26quot%3Bcreates%20real%20uncertainty%20for%20our%20team%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGitLab%20employees%20are%20the%20latest%20group%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-employees-face-layoffs-tough-choice-hustle-job-hunt-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esweating%20it%20out%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20they%20wait%20to%20learn%20whether%20they%20dodged%20the%20layoff%20blade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20software%20company%2C%20which%20had%202%2C580%20employees%20as%20of%20January%2C%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20was%20restructuring%20to%20meet%20%26quot%3Bthe%20agentic%20era%26quot%3B%20and%20planned%20to%20cut%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20its%20workforce%20by%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20in%20the%20company%20fell%207%25%20after%20hours%20following%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGitLab%20CEO%20Bill%20Staples%20wrote%20in%20a%20memo%20to%20employees%20and%20investors%20that%20the%20restructuring%20would%20happen%20%26quot%3Bopenly%26quot%3B%20and%20entail%20flattening%20the%20org%20chart%20%E2%80%94%20removing%20%26quot%3Bup%20to%20three%20layers%20of%20management%20so%20leaders%20are%20closer%20to%20the%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20research%20and%20development%20teams%20will%20be%20reorganized%20into%20around%2060%20%26quot%3Bsmaller%2C%20more%20empowered%20teams%20with%20end-to-end%20ownership%2C%26quot%3B%20Staples%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20agents%20will%20also%20be%20embedded%20into%20GitLab's%20internal%20processes%2C%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3Bautomating%20the%20reviews%2C%20approvals%2C%20and%20handoffs%20to%20speed%20us%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20means%20the%20company%20will%20%26quot%3Bright-size%26quot%3B%20roles%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20said%20that%20GitLab%2C%20which%20makes%20a%20software%20platform%20to%20help%20coders%20manage%20projects%20and%20tasks%2C%20is%20evolving%20its%20strategy%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20future%20state%20of%20software%20engineering.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20cost%20of%20producing%20software%20collapses%2C%20demand%20for%20it%20will%20expand.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20developer%20platform%20market%20used%20to%20be%20measured%20in%20tens%20of%20dollars%20per%20user%20per%20month%2C%20this%20year%20it%20is%20hundreds%2Fuser%2Fmonth%20and%20headed%20to%20thousands%2C%26quot%3B%20Staples%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20state%20of%20developer%20industry%20itself%2C%20GitLab's%20CEO%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20supply%20of%20deep%20technical%20problems%20is%20multiplying%2C%20and%20the%20engineers%20who%20can%20solve%20them%20will%20be%20among%20the%20scarcest%20and%20most%20valuable%20talent%20in%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20GitLab%20CEO%20Bill%20Staples'%20memo%20to%20employees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1f98ef6-162a-48f7-a378-295b44e5838e%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGitLab%20Act%202%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20letter%20to%20our%20customers%20and%20our%20investors.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe've%20been%20working%20through%20some%20significant%20changes%20inside%20GitLab%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20share%20them%20with%20you%20directly.%20The%20email%20I%20sent%20the%20team%20is%20included%20below%20for%20full%20context.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20agentic%20era%20affords%20GitLab%20the%20largest%20opportunity%20in%20our%20history%20as%20a%20company%2C%20and%20we're%20making%20the%20structural%20and%20strategic%20decisions%20to%20meet%20it.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20letter%20has%20three%20parts.%20First%2C%20the%20operational%20and%20structural%20news%2C%20which%20is%20hard.%20Second%2C%20the%20strategic%20thesis%20we're%20betting%20on.%20And%20finally%2C%20what%20this%20means%20specifically%20for%20you%2C%20our%20customers%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286bb00dc-14ea-4e47-b5df-adb46393d01b%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20structural%20news%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20morning%20we%20shared%20with%20team%20members%20that%20we're%20beginning%20a%20restructuring%20process%20at%20GitLab%2C%20and%20we're%20running%20it%20differently%20than%20most.%20The%20planning%20is%20happening%20openly%2C%20including%20a%20voluntary%20separation%20window.%20That%20creates%20real%20uncertainty%20for%20our%20team%20over%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20but%20we%20believe%20the%20outcome%20will%20be%20better%20for%20it.%20Where%20we%20can%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20finalize%20the%20new%20shape%20of%20the%20company%20on%20or%20before%20June%201.%20Where%20local%20requirements%20apply%20we%20will%20not%20make%20any%20changes%20until%20the%20local%20process%20is%20complete.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFour%20operational%20changes%20are%20part%20of%20the%20workforce%20reduction.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.%20We're%20reevaluating%20our%20operational%20footprint%2C%20and%20are%20planning%20to%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20countries%20by%20up%20to%2030%25%20where%20we%20have%20small%20teams.%20We'll%20continue%20serving%20customers%20in%20those%20markets%20through%20our%20partner%20network.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E2.%20We're%20planning%20to%20flatten%20the%20organization%2C%20removing%20up%20to%20three%20layers%20of%20management%20in%20some%20functions%20so%20leaders%20are%20closer%20to%20the%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E3.%20We're%20re-organizing%20R%26amp%3BD%20to%20create%20roughly%2060%20smaller%2C%20more%20empowered%20teams%20with%20end-to-end%20ownership%2C%20nearly%20doubling%20the%20number%20of%20independent%20teams.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E4.%20We're%20rewiring%20internal%20processes%20with%20AI%20agents%2C%20automating%20the%20reviews%2C%20approvals%2C%20and%20handoffs%20to%20speed%20us%20up%2C%20and%20plan%20to%20right-size%20roles%20across%20the%20company%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOperational%20changes%20and%20the%20update%20to%20our%20strategy%20are%20happening%20together%3A%20they%20are%20related%20but%20independent.%20Operationally%2C%20we%20grew%20into%20a%20shape%20that%20was%20right%20for%20the%20last%20era%20and%20isn't%20right%20for%20this%20one.%20The%20strategy%20below%20is%20what%20we're%20betting%20on%20next%2C%20and%20stands%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20are%20reaffirming%20our%20Q1%20and%20full%20year%20FY27%20guidance%20today.%20The%20final%20scope%20and%20financial%20impact%20of%20the%20restructuring%20will%20be%20shared%20on%20our%20June%202%20earnings%20call%2C%20once%20we've%20finished%20the%20plan%20and%20received%20approval%20by%20our%20board.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e9a71b0-4312-45ad-85ec-798d82d19ad1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOur%20Core%20Beliefs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnderpinning%20the%20changes%20we're%20making%20today%2C%20and%20our%20go%20forward%20strategy%20are%2010%20core%20beliefs%20that%20span%20the%20world%20we're%20building%20for%2C%20the%20architectural%20bets%20we're%20making%20and%20how%20we'll%20deliver.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e3d998e0-a075-4ef5-8dbd-1b679ca470fe%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20world%20we're%20building%20for%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe're%20evolving%20our%20strategy%20to%20optimize%20for%20the%20future%20state%20of%20software%20engineering%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E1-%20Software%20will%20be%20built%20by%20machines%2C%20directed%20by%20people.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20AI%20is%20the%20substrate%20on%20which%20future%20software%20gets%20built.%20Agents%20will%20plan%2C%20code%2C%20review%2C%20deploy%2C%20and%20repair.%20Humans%20still%20own%20the%20judgment%20that%20matters%20most%3A%20architecture%2C%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20customer%20problem%2C%20the%20tradeoffs%20that%20require%20taste.%20This%20is%20why%20we%20built%20and%20released%20the%20Duo%20Agent%20Platform%20in%20January.%20Our%20first%20quarter%20adoption%20is%20promising%2C%20and%20we're%20ready%20to%20accelerate.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E2-%20The%20agentic%20era%20multiplies%20demand%20for%20software.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Software%20has%20been%20the%20force%20multiplier%20behind%20nearly%20every%20business%20transformation%20of%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20The%20constraint%20was%20the%20cost%20and%20time%20of%20producing%20and%20managing%20it.%20That%20constraint%20is%20collapsing.%20As%20the%20cost%20of%20producing%20software%20collapses%2C%20demand%20for%20it%20will%20expand.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20developer%20platform%20market%20used%20to%20be%20measured%20in%20tens%20of%20dollars%20per%20user%20per%20month%2C%20this%20year%20it%20is%20hundreds%2Fuser%2Fmonth%20and%20headed%20to%20thousands.%20Not%20only%20is%20the%20value%20of%20software%20for%20builders%20increasing%2C%20but%20we%20believe%20there%20will%20be%20more%20software%20and%20builders%20than%20ever%2C%20and%20we%20will%20serve%20an%20increasing%20volume%20of%20both.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E3-%20The%20consequential%20work%20belongs%20to%20engineers.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Engineering%20has%20always%20been%20about%20more%20than%20writing%20code.%20Great%20engineers%20are%20problem%20solvers%20and%20builders%20who%20care%20about%20system%20design%2C%20distributed%20systems%2C%20reasoning%20through%20failures%2C%20safely%20integrating%20new%20capability%20into%20critical%20systems%2C%20and%20making%20decisions%20under%20ambiguity.%20These%20are%20exactly%20the%20skills%20the%20agentic%20era%20needs%20more%20of%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20volume%20of%20software%20increases.%20The%20supply%20of%20deep%20technical%20problems%20is%20multiplying%2C%20and%20the%20engineers%20who%20can%20solve%20them%20will%20be%20among%20the%20scarcest%20and%20most%20valuable%20talent%20in%20the%20market.%20Our%20core%20users'%20roles%20are%20evolving%2C%20their%20importance%20is%20only%20increasing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f45f51a-8777-49d3-bd97-2639d92abbae%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20architectural%20bets%20we're%20making%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPlatforms%20that%20weren't%20built%20for%20machine%20scale%20are%20starting%20to%20break%20under%20it.%20Winning%20means%20investing%20in%20the%20fundamentals%20that%20really%20matter%3A%20security%2C%20performance%2C%20scalability%2C%20reliability%20and%20user%20experience.%20We're%20making%20five%2C%20fundamental%20architectural%20bets.%20Each%20one%20is%20underway%20and%20we%20plan%20to%20deliver%20without%20disruption%20to%20GitLab%20customers%20that%20depend%20on%20us%20every%20day.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E4-%20Machine-scale%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Agents%20open%20merge%20requests%20in%20parallel%2C%20trigger%20pipelines%20around%20the%20clock%2C%20and%20push%20commits%20at%20a%20rate%20no%20human%20team%20ever%20did.%20Git%20itself%20wasn't%20designed%20for%20that%20load%2C%20and%20bolting%20AI%20onto%20platforms%20not%20built%20for%20agents%20is%20the%20biggest%20mistake%20of%20this%20era.%20We're%20doing%20a%20generational%20rebuild%20of%20the%20underlying%20infrastructure%20to%20handle%20agent-rate%20work%20as%20the%20default.%20Git%20itself%20is%20being%20reengineered%20for%20machine%20scale.%20The%20monolith%20is%20giving%20way%20to%20modern%2C%20API-first%2C%20composable%20services.%20And%20agent-specific%20APIs%20are%20being%20built%20so%20agents%20can%20act%20as%20first-class%20users%20of%20the%20platform%2C%20not%20as%20bolted-on%20consumers%20of%20human-shaped%20interfaces.%20The%20value%20of%20this%20100x%20scale%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20reliability%20and%20performance%20it%20provides%20is%20much%20higher%20than%20the%20generation%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20market%20today.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E5-%20Orchestration%20across%20the%20full%20lifecycle.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20A%20single%20agent%20that%20writes%20code%20or%20opens%20a%20merge%20request%20produces%20activity.%20Enterprises%20don't%20need%20agent%20activity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThey%20need%20running%20software%20that%20moves%20the%20business%20forward.%20Orchestration%20is%20the%20layer%20that%20gets%20you%20there.%20It%20coordinates%20agents%20across%20the%20lifecycle%2C%20assigning%20work%2C%20managing%20state%2C%20passing%20context%2C%20resolving%20conflicts%2C%20enforcing%20policy%2C%20and%20keeping%20a%20human%20in%20the%20loop%20when%20it%20matters.%20CI%2FCD%20is%20one%20of%20the%20components%20getting%20reimagined.%20The%20GitLab%20pipeline%20was%20designed%20to%20take%20human-rate%20commits%20and%20ship%20them%20safely%3B%20in%20the%20agentic%20era%20our%20orchestration%20service%20becomes%20the%20runtime%20that%20coordinates%20agents%2C%20validates%20the%20work%20and%20enforces%20guardrails%2C%20and%20drives%20change%20all%20the%20way%20to%20production%20at%20machine%20rate.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E6-%20Context%20is%20our%20superpower.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3EEvery%20dev%20tool%20vendor%20is%20converging%20on%20similar%20code%20generation%20capabilities.%20Enterprise%20AI%20bills%20are%20climbing%20as%20fast%20as%20adoption.%20What%20doesn't%20commoditize%20is%20the%20unique%20context%20the%20model%20gets%20to%20work%20with%3A%20a%20data%20model%20that%20connects%20planning%2C%20code%2C%20review%2C%20security%2C%20deployment%2C%20and%20operations%20across%20every%20project%20and%20repository%2C%20accumulated%20over%20years%20of%20a%20team's%20work.%20We're%20investing%20in%20that%20connected%20data%20model%20as%20a%20first-class%2C%20API-accessible%20service%2C%20and%20it%20delivers%20more%20value%20with%20every%20human%20and%20agent%20action.%20Context%20is%20what%20lets%20agents%20spend%20fewer%20tokens%20and%20deliver%20better%20results.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E7-%20Governance%20built%20into%20the%20core.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Governance%20is%20what%20lets%20enterprises%20move%20fast%20in%20the%20agentic%20era.%20Like%20a%20race%20car%2C%20it%20doesn't%20matter%20how%20fast%20you%20can%20go%20if%20you%20can't%20maintain%20control.%20As%20agents%20take%20on%20more%20of%20the%20work%2C%20enterprises%20need%20a%20platform%20that%20can%20enforce%20who's%20allowed%20to%20do%20what%2C%20prove%20what%20happened%20and%20why%2C%20and%20keep%20sensitive%20code%20and%20data%20where%20it%20belongs.%20We're%20building%20identity%2C%20audit%2C%20policy%2C%20and%20deployment%20flexibility%20as%20core%20platform%20services%20that%20every%20agent%2C%20pipeline%2C%20and%20merge%20request%20runs%20through%20by%20default%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20separate%20product%20layered%20on%20top.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E8-%20One%20platform%2C%20three%20modes.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Trillions%20of%20lines%20of%20code%20run%20the%20world's%20businesses%20today.%20Rewriting%20most%20of%20it%20is%20too%20risky%20and%20too%20expensive%20to%20justify.%20The%20cloud%20era%20taught%20us%20enterprises%20run%20hybrid%2C%20and%20operating%20across%20that%20mix%20has%20been%20painful%2C%20expensive%2C%20and%20never%20fully%20solved.%20The%20agentic%20era%20will%20be%20the%20same.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEvery%20enterprise%20will%20live%20across%20a%20spectrum%20of%20human-owned%2C%20agent-assisted%2C%20and%20agent-autonomous%20work.%20We're%20building%20one%20platform%2C%20one%20data%20model%2C%20one%20governance%20system%20that%20operates%20across%20all%20three%20modes%2C%20and%20delivering%20it%20cloud%20and%20model%20neutral.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fbc54d42-25d5-430c-b5a5-16e3c65b62f6%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20we'll%20deliver%20it%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E9-%20A%20flexible%20business%20model.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20As%20the%20way%20software%20gets%20built%20changes%2C%20the%20business%20model%20must%20evolve%20with%20it.%20Agentic%20AI%20can%20augment%20teams%2C%20perform%20real%20work%20and%20the%20business%20model%20must%20scale%20with%20the%20cost%20and%20value%20of%20the%20work%20performed.%20We're%20keeping%20what%20works%3A%20the%20predictability%20of%20subscriptions%20for%20what%20customers%20have%20today.%20We've%20already%20added%20consumption%20pricing%20for%20the%20work%20agents%20do%2C%20with%20other%20major%20players%20following%20over%20the%20past%20few%20months.%20Next%2C%20we're%20introducing%20more%20flexibility%20to%20mix%20both%20as%20the%20way%20of%20work%20evolves.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E10-%20Culture%20of%20excellence.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Operational%20character%20is%20a%20key%20differentiator.%20What%20matters%20most%20right%20now%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20move%20quickly%2C%20own%20outcomes%2C%20and%20deliver%20real%20value%20to%20our%20customers.%20Speed%20with%20Quality%2C%20Ownership%20Mindset%2C%20and%20Customer%20Outcomes%20are%20our%20new%20operating%20principles%2C%20built%20on%20a%20culture%20of%20excellence.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2215f676db-cb9a-4aa5-9204-2578d8cd936a%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20our%20customers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20our%20customers%2C%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20today%20is%20what%20doesn't%20change.%20The%20support%2C%20roadmap%20commitments%2C%20contractual%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20it%20continues%20without%20disruption.%20Your%20account%20team%20is%20available%20to%20walk%20you%20through%20today's%20news%20if%20you'd%20like%20a%20conversation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWhere%20you%20should%20expect%20to%20see%20us%20evolve%20is%20in%20the%20quality%2C%20depth%20and%20pace%20of%20innovation%20we%20ship.%20We%20will%20lead%20the%20way%20in%20agentic%20engineering%20by%20being%20customer%20zero%20of%20our%20platform%2C%20demonstrating%20with%20our%20innovation%20and%20our%20results%20the%20success%20you%20can%20bet%20on%20as%20our%20customers.%20Our%20vision%20for%20the%20product%20and%20business%20model%20is%20clearer%20than%20it%20has%20ever%20been%20and%20we're%20accelerating%20the%20work.%20We'll%20share%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20our%20innovation%20roadmap%20at%20GitLab%20Transcend%20on%20June%2010%2C%202026%20and%20hope%20you'll%20join%20us.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b0714e1c-62ce-4adb-8abb-a59f18820501%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20our%20investors%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EToday's%20announcement%20is%20a%20deliberate%20move%20to%20lead%20in%20a%20market%20we%20believe%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20its%20largest%20shift%20in%20twenty%20years.%20The%20opportunity%20here%20isn't%20incremental%20growth%20on%20a%20DevSecOps%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20we're%20building%20toward%20becoming%20the%20trusted%20enterprise%20platform%20for%20software%20creation%20in%20the%20AI%20era.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20look%20forward%20to%20sharing%20an%20update%20on%20the%20business%20and%20our%20Q1%20results%20in%20our%20upcoming%20earnings%20call%20on%20June%202%2C%202026.%20We'll%20also%20share%20the%20final%20scope%20and%20financial%20impact%20of%20the%20restructuring%20at%20that%20time%2C%20although%20we%20anticipate%20reinvesting%20the%20majority%20of%20savings%20into%20accelerating%20our%20progress%20against%20the%20specific%20growth%20and%20technological%20initiatives%20that%20we've%20outlined.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20most%20consequential%20work%20we've%20taken%20on%20as%20a%20company.%20We'll%20prove%20it%20in%20the%20innovation%20we%20bring%20to%20market%2C%20how%20we%20serve%20our%20customers%2C%20and%20how%20we%20create%20value%20for%20our%20shareholders%20over%20the%20near-%20and%20long-term.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThank%20you%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E-Bill%20Staples%20CEO%2C%20GitLab%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgitlab-layoffs-memo-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778544449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a025f23c9dd4cb81cda95fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgitlab-layoffs-memo-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22GitLab's%20CEO%20told%20employees%20the%20restructuring%20means%20layoffs%2C%20flatter%20structure%2C%20smaller%20teams%2C%20an