AmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20Trump-Xi%20summit%20could%20set%20superpower%20relations%20for%20many%20years%20to%20come%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778541653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fbf89%2Flive%2F32ca6120-4d37-11f1-b55d-0f258dce1735.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fceqprgen1nyo%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20whirlwind%20visit%20to%20China%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20for%20years%20-%20but%20will%20it%20bear%20fruit%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fceqprgen1nyo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BuzzFeed's%20fire%20sale%20to%20Byron%20Allen%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20an%20era%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228095%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Byron%20Allen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024728ba7ef34b41f372fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EByron%20Allen%20wanted%20to%20buy%20Paramount.%20Now%20he's%20buying%20a%20controlling%20stake%20in%20BuzzFeed.%3Cp%3EParas%20Griffin%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGo%20back%20in%20time%20to%202016%3A%20BuzzFeed%2C%20Vice%20Media%2C%20and%20Vox%20Media%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20future%20of%20media.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENow%20back%20to%20present%20tense%3A%20Vice%20filed%20for%20Chapter%2011%2C%20Vox%20is%20breaking%20up%2C%20and%20BuzzFeed%20just%20sold%20itself%20for%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20former%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeanwhile%2C%20many%20of%20the%20companies%20the%20digital%20upstarts%20were%20supposed%20to%20replace%20%E2%80%94%20big%20publishers%20and%20TV%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20are%20still%20here.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20BuzzFeed%20was%20the%20future%20of%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202026%2C%20BuzzFeed%20looks%20just%20about%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20digital%20publisher%20told%20investors%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.buzzfeed.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbuzzfeed-inc-reports-q4-and-full-year-2025-results%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erunning%20out%20of%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20looking%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrategic%20options.%26quot%3B%20On%20Monday%2C%20it%20announced%20the%20option%20it%20settled%20on%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finvestors.buzzfeed.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fbuzzfeed-inc-announces-proposed-majority-stake-investment-byron%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20will%20sell%20a%20majority%20stake%20to%20media%20entrepreneur%20Byron%20Allen%20for%20%24120%20million%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20can%20talk%20about%20the%20deal%2C%20slated%20to%20close%20later%20this%20month%2C%20in%20a%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20first%2C%20the%20requisite%20big%20picture%3A%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20BuzzFeed%2C%20along%20with%20other%20digital%20upstarts%20like%20Vice%20and%20Vox%20Media%2C%20was%20the%20new%20model%20for%20media.%20The%20pitch%3A%20These%20guys%20were%20digital%20natives%20who%20understood%20how%20to%20make%20stuff%20millennials%20liked%2C%20and%20they%20understood%20how%20to%20work%20with%20big%20internet%20platforms%20%E2%80%94%20Facebook%2C%20in%20particular%20%E2%80%94%20which%20were%20growing%20like%20a%20weed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20big%20media%20companies%20like%20Comcast%2C%20Disney%2C%20and%20Fox%20%E2%80%94%20loved%20the%20concept%2C%20and%20valued%20the%20companies%20like%20high-flying%20tech%20startups.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Vox%20was%20worth%20%241%20billion%2C%20BuzzFeed%20was%20worth%20%241.7%20billion%2C%20and%20Vice%20was%20theoretically%20worth%20%245.7%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20turn%20was%20pretty%20quick%3A%20Facebook%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20more%20of%20a%20competitor%20than%20a%20partner%2C%20digital%20advertising%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20very%20difficult%20business%2C%20and%20investors%20lost%20their%20taste%20for%20the%20whole%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20former%20high-flying%20publishers%20went%20through%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20layoffs%2C%20and%20Vice%20filed%20for%20bankruptcy%20protection.%20Vox%20Media%20seems%20close%20to%20selling%20itself%20off%20in%20parts%2C%20and%20James%20Murdoch's%20Lupa%20Systems%20seems%20likely%20to%20buy%20Vox's%20podcast%20network%20and%20its%20New%20York%20magazine%20title%20(Disclosure%3A%20Vox%20produces%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fchannels-with-peter-kafka%2Fid1080467174%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChannels%3C%2Fa%3E%20podcast.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-buzzfeed-july-15-deadline-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuzzFeed%2C%20which%20spent%20part%20of%202024%20fending%20off%20a%20hostile%20takeover%20from%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%2C%20is%20waving%20the%20white%20flag%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22BuzzFeed%20website%20on%20a%20laptop%20screen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a025d80c9dd4cb81cda95e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuzzFeed%20was%20once%20a%20digital%20darling.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20why%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbyron-allen-media-group-buy-paramount-offer-why-streaming-tv-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EByron%20Allen%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20media%20personality%20who%20periodically%20pops%20up%20to%20announce%20he%20wants%20to%20buy%20a%20giant%20media%20property%20like%20Paramount%2C%20but%20seldom%20does%20%E2%80%94%20going%20to%20buy%20BuzzFeed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20got%20me.%20In%20the%20press%20release%20announcing%20the%20deal%2C%20Allen%20says%20he%20wants%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20on%20the%20iconic%20foundation%20of%20BuzzFeed%20and%20HuffPost%20by%20expanding%20into%20free-streaming%20video%2C%20audio%2C%20and%20user-generated%20content%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20pretty%20close%20to%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-buzzfeed-july-15-deadline-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERamaswamy%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20do%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Allen%20also%20says%20that%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20power%20of%20AI%2C%20BuzzFeed%20is%20officially%20chasing%20YouTube%20to%20become%20another%20premiere%20free%20video%20streaming%20service%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that's%20just%20not%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20can%20say%20is%20that%20for%20at%20least%20a%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.complex.com%2Fpop-culture%2Fa%2Fbernadette-giacomazzo%2Fstephen-colbert-byron-allen-late-show%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAllen%20will%20be%20programming%20the%20CBS%20late-night%20slot%20left%20empty%20by%20Stephen%20Colbert's%20departure%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%20while%20he%20doesn't%20own%20Paramount%2C%20he%20can%20at%20least%20say%20he's%20got%20some%20shows%20on%20the%20company's%20broadcast%20network%2C%20and%20he%20owns%20a%20digital%20property%20that%20was%20white%20hot%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20what%20about%20the%20deal%20Allen%20has%20struck%3F%20That%20one%20is%20a%20little%20confusing%2C%20too.%20The%20headline%20price%20is%20%24120%20million%20for%2052%25%20of%20the%20company's%20shares.%20But%20that%20really%20means%20%2420%20million%20in%20cash%20up%20front%2C%20plus%20a%20promise%20to%20pay%20another%20%24100%20million%2C%20plus%20interest%2C%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20that's%20a%20good%20deal%20or%20not%20may%20depend%20on%20your%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20Monday's%20announcement%2C%20BuzzFeed's%20market%20cap%20was%20less%20than%20%2430%20million%20%E2%80%94%20which%20suggests%20that%20Allen%20is%20paying%2010%20times%20more%20for%20BuzzFeed%20than%20the%20market%20thinks%20it's%20worth.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20BuzzFeed%20would%20claim%20that%20it's%20really%20worth%20much%20more%20than%20its%20stock%20suggests%2C%20because%20it%20is%20weighed%20down%20with%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20debt%20is%20still%20here%2C%20and%20BuzzFeed's%20current%20financial%20performance%20is%20pretty%20dire%3A%20In%20its%20most%20recent%20quarter%2C%20revenue%20declined%2012.4%25%2C%20to%20%2431.6%20million%2C%20and%20its%20losses%20increased%2021%25%2C%20to%20%2415.1%20million.%20Couple%20that%20with%20March's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGoing_concern%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20concern%3C%2Fa%3E%20note%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flashing%20red%20light%20telling%20investors%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20doubt%26quot%3B%20it%20could%20last%20another%20year%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20should%20end%20up%20with%20a%20fire-sale%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20Allen%20be%20right%2C%20and%20BuzzFeed%20really%20is%20worth%20more%20than%20Wall%20Street%20thinks%3F%20Sure%2C%20I%20guess.%20Maybe%20with%20Allen%20in%20charge%2C%20BuzzFeed%20will%20undergo%20even%20more%20cuts%20%E2%80%94%20perhaps%20cuts%20Jonah%20Peretti%2C%20the%20company's%20founder%2C%20was%20unwilling%20to%20make%20for%20emotional%20reasons.%20Maybe%20the%20brand%20BuzzFeed%20built%20up%20in%20its%20earlier%20incarnation%20still%20means%20something%20to%20enough%20people%2C%20and%20Allen%20can%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20leverage%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe'll%20see!%20The%20only%20thing%20we%20know%20for%20sure%20is%20that%20this%20isn't%20the%20future%20of%20media%20that%20Peretti%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%20thought%20we%20were%20getting%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-why-byron-allen-buying-peretti-vox-vice-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778540548000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a024781e1443b8dc48e40ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-why-byron-allen-buying-peretti-vox-vice-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BuzzFeed%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20future%20of%20media.%20But%20that%20future%20wasn't%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20last-ditch%20sale.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20research%20suggests%20cancer%20may%20develop%20earlier%20than%20we%20thought%20%E2%80%94%20but%20simple%20changes%20can%20help%20prevent%20it%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20young%20person%20laying%20on%20a%20medical%20table%20for%20an%20MRI%20scan%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a022adbc9dd4cb81cda943c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20research%20is%20a%20step%20closer%20to%20individual%20assessments%20of%20cancer%20risk%20that%20can%20help%20younger%20people%20get%20life-saving%20scans%20or%20screenings.%3Cp%3Eshironosov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20new%20study%20on%20more%20than%20100%20risk%20factors%20for%20cancer%20sheds%20light%20on%20why%20some%20people%20get%20a%20diagnosis%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearchers%20say%20it%20could%20help%20us%20develop%20customized%20action%20plans%20to%20prevent%20and%20diagnose%20cancer%20sooner.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHelpful%20habits%20to%20stave%20off%20cancer%20include%20eating%20more%20fatty%20fish%20and%20drinking%20coffee%20or%20tea.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECancer%20screening%20can%20feel%20like%20a%20rite%20of%20passage%20as%20we%20get%20older%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F21-year-old-skin-cancer-melanoma-doctors-missed-symptoms-mole-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eskin%20cancer%20checks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20your%20late%2030s%2C%20a%20mammogram%20at%20age%2040%2C%20a%20colonoscopy%20at%20age%2045.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrue-cost-young-colon-cancer-crisis-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eyoung%20cancer%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20skyrocketed%2C%20the%20previous%20screening%20guidelines%20are%20becoming%20increasingly%20too%20late%20for%20patients%20who%20develop%20symptoms%20in%20their%2020s%20or%20early%2030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20nuanced%20approach%20could%20help%20calculate%20each%20person's%20unique%20risk%20of%20cancer%20and%20find%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20prevent%20it%20or%20detect%20it%20early%20enough%20for%20treatment%2C%20a%20new%20study%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20study%2C%20Dr.%20Neel%20Butala%2C%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20School%20of%20Medicine%20and%20cofounder%20of%20Catch%2C%20a%20cancer%20risk%20assessment%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAge%20is%20like%20the%20best%20thing%20we%20have%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20crude%20proxy%20for%20cancer%20risk.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20other%20things%20going%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Butala%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20research%20points%20toward%20how%20to%20personalize%20cancer%20prevention%20and%20reduce%20risk%20by%20optimizing%20lifestyle%20habits%20like%20diet%20and%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBehavior%20change%20is%20hard%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20like%20you%20need%20to%20be%20a%20superhuman%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20Butala%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20this%20positive%20message%20that%20change%20at%20any%20age%20can%20actually%20reduce%20your%20cancer%20risk%20a%20fair%20amount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e0a5c506-97c9-41c9-8a3f-1da9b8ff122e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUnderstanding%20cancer%20risk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20better%20understand%20why%20some%20people%20get%20cancer%20and%20others%20don't%2C%20Butala%20and%20colleagues%20from%20Stanford%2C%20Harvard%2C%20and%20other%20universities%20looked%20at%20potential%20risk%20factors%20for%2021%20of%20the%20most%20common%20cancers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20created%20a%20model%20to%20assess%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-4-in-10-cancers-preventable-ways-to-lower-risk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20a%20lifetime%20based%20on%20a%20list%20of%20more%20than%20100%20factors%20ranging%20from%20drinking%20habits%20to%20medical%20history%20to%20over-the-counter%20medication%20and%20supplement%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22fiber%20supplement%20with%20water%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f38c5997df9f8cd3cd3d08%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20new%20study%20looked%20at%20100%20risk%20factors%20for%20cancer%2C%20ranging%20from%20supplement%20use%20to%20drinking%20habits.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Blottman%20Photography%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat's%20beautiful%20about%20the%20model%20is%20that%20we%20actually%20can%20incorporate%20all%20these%20at%20once%E2%80%A6and%20then%20quantify%20individual%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Butala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20found%20that%20while%20cancer%20risk%20tends%20to%20increase%20as%20we%20get%20older%20overall%2C%20some%20people's%20risk%20accelerates%20more%20quickly%20based%20on%20their%20lifestyle%20and%20health%20history.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20healthy%2070-year-old%20woman%20can%20be%20less%20prone%20to%20cancer%20than%20a%20high-risk%20woman%20in%20her%2040s.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20published%20in%20a%20paper%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fascopubs.org%2Fdoi%2F10.1200%2FOA-25-00209%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJCO%20Oncology%20Advances%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20month%2C%20included%20people%20from%20ages%2040%20to%2070%2C%20so%20it%20doesn't%20specifically%20address%20cancer%20cases%20among%20people%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s.%20Still%2C%20it%20helps%20explain%20why%20current%20best%20practices%20can%20miss%20potential%20early-onset%20cancers%20and%20could%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20people%20to%20access%20life-saving%20scans%2C%20tests%2C%20or%20treatments%20sooner%2C%20Butala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20good%20conversation%20starter%20for%20doctors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20on%20the%20extreme%20end%20of%20risk%2C%20we%20provide%20evidence%20and%20how%20you%20can%20talk%20to%20your%20doctor%20about%20'Maybe%20I%20need%20a%20colonoscopy%20at%20an%20earlier%20age.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20patients%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-so-many-young-people-getting-colon-cancer-answer-infancy-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eearly-onset%20colon%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20have%20said%20they%20struggled%20to%20get%20a%20colonoscopy%20because%20medical%20staff%20thought%20they%20were%20too%20young.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20some%20patients%20aren't%20diagnosed%20until%20later%20stages%2C%20when%20the%20cancer%20has%20spread%20and%20is%20harder%20to%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EButala%20said%20that%20individualized%20cancer%20assessments%20could%20also%20help%20people%20make%20healthier%20lifestyle%20choices%20tailored%20to%20their%20specific%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20risk%20reduction%2C%20it's%20like%20an%20action%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20Butala%20said.%20%26quot%3BShowing%20people%20the%20lifetime%20impact%20of%20their%20behaviors%20can%20actually%20reduce%20the%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223c7f1cf9-0cf2-42e3-b6eb-f98c1179f031%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20habits%20to%20prevent%20cancer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EButala%20said%20a%20major%20takeaway%20of%20the%20study%20is%20that%20cancer%20risk%20isn't%20inevitable%2C%20and%20healthier%20habits%20can%20help%20lower%20the%20risk%20of%20cancer%20as%20we%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20your%2060s%2C%20if%20you%20modify%20your%20behavior%2C%20you%20end%20up%20looking%20like%E2%80%A6%20you're%20in%20your%2050s%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20overhaul%20your%20life%20or%20optimize%20every%20decision%20to%20benefit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETo%20reduce%20your%20cancer%20risk%2C%20the%20research%20suggests%20starting%20with%20these%20simple%20habits%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEat%20at%20least%20two%20servings%20of%20fruit%20or%20veggies%20a%20day%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffishwife-sardines-protein-content-most-popular-fish-influencers-recipes-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEat%20more%20fatty%20fish%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EExercise%20for%20about%2030%20minutes%20a%20day%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECut%20back%20on%20processed%20foods%2C%20added%20sugar%2C%20and%20salt%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoffee-best-ingredient-longevity-kitchen-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDrink%20coffee%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20tea%20daily%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStay%20hydrated%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20cancer%20risk%20rises%20as%20we%20age%2C%20older%20adults%20might%20benefit%20even%20more%20from%20making%20changes%2C%20according%20to%20Butala.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20age%20at%20which%20it's%20too%20late%20to%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BOver%20a%20lifetime%2C%20starting%20earlier%20makes%