nounced%20the%20creation%20of%20stand-alone%20company%2C%20OpenAI%20Deployment%20Company%2C%20that%20it%20said%20is%20%26quot%3Bdesigned%20to%20help%20organizations%20build%20and%20deploy%20AI%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20and%2019%20other%20companies%2C%20including%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-marco-argenti-ai-engineers-developers-effectiveness-productivity-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Goldman%20Sachs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Brookfield%2C%20and%20Bain%20Capital%2C%20partnered%20to%20create%20the%20new%20firm.%20The%20deployment%20company%20will%20launch%20with%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20more%20than%20%244%20billion%20at%20a%20%2410%20billion%20pre-money%20valuation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20announcement%2C%20OpenAI%20said%20it%20had%20acquired%20Tomoro%2C%20an%20applied%20AI%20consulting%20and%20engineering%20firm%2C%20which%20will%20give%20the%20new%20OpenAI%20firm%20a%20foundation%20of%20roughly%20150%20Forward%20Deployed%20Engineers%20(FDEs).%20Popularized%20by%20Palantir%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-job-ai-forward-deployed-engineer-skills-need-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFDEs%20have%20become%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20AI%20economy%2C%20as%20big%20companies%20push%20for%20AI%20tools%20specifically%20tailored%20to%20their%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20what%20AI%20and%20tech%20experts%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20new%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Box%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie%20on%20stage.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a01c5f0ba7ef34b41f36eec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222670%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBox%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c246814c-c4c9-4357-b402-431411067885%5C%22%3EAaron%20Levie%2C%20CEO%20of%20Box%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBox%20CEO%20Aaron%20Levie%20said%20there%20is%20a%20big%20need%20for%20services%20and%20forward-deployed%20engineers%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20an%20insane%20amount%20of%20technical%20and%20domain-specific%20process%20work%20to%20be%20done%20to%20make%20this%20all%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Levie%20wrote%20on%20X%2C%20commenting%20on%20OpenAI's%20announcement.%20%26quot%3BHuge%20opportunity%20for%20new%20service%20providers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20internally%20teams%20and%20roles%20to%20emerge%2C%20to%20help%20drive%20this%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELevie%20stressed%20that%20none%20of%20the%20changes%20required%20for%20businesses%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20agentic%20AI%20moment%20%26quot%3Bis%20easy%20technically.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20first%20modernize%20your%20infrastructure%20and%20data%20and%20make%20sure%20it's%20ready%20for%20agents%3B%20access%20controls%2C%20entitlements%2C%20and%20permissions%20need%20to%20be%20mapped%20in%20a%20way%20that%20works%20for%20agents%20and%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20agents%20have%20the%20right%20context%20to%20work%20with%3B%20you%20need%20to%20consistently%20eval%20and%20maintain%20the%20agents%20when%20there%20are%20model%20upgrades%3B%20and%20you%20need%20to%20drive%20the%20change%20management%20of%20the%20process%20itself%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20parts%20the%20people%20do%20and%20what%20agents%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224608%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NVIDIA%20sign%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fe0f6fe1443b8dc48e347d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20announcement%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20an%20Nvidia%20VP.%3Cp%3EGina%20Hsu%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22abcc9eda-e771-447f-baf7-5b45605c3558%5C%22%3ESunny%20Madra%2C%20Vice%20President%20of%