_articleshow%2F131023672.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20paid%20%24102%2C000%20for%20a%20facelift%20at%2071.%20I%20wish%20I%20could%20have%20done%20it%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20afford%20it.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20before%20and%20after%20a%20facelift.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0224f7ba7ef34b41f3716c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarolyn%20Rudolph%20in%20clinic%20pictures%20before%20and%20after%20her%20facelift.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dr.%20Carl%20Truesdale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECarolyn%20Rudolph%20waited%20until%20she%20was%2071%20to%20have%20a%20full%20facelift%20that%20cost%20over%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20she%20couldn't%20have%20paid%20for%20it%20in%20her%2060s%2C%20but%20wishes%20she'd%20been%20able%20to%20have%20it%20earlier.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20great-grandmother%20is%20pleased%20with%20the%20results%2C%20but%20said%20some%20of%20her%20friendships%20had%20changed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20interview%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Carolyn%20Rudoph%2C%2073%2C%20retired%20Army%20personnel%20and%20postal%20supervisor%2C%20from%20Louisville%2C%20Kentucky.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20always%20kept%20myself%20in%20shape%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F87-year-old-cyclist-fitness-diet-secrets-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egoing%20to%20the%20gym%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20maintaining%20a%20size%206%2C%20and%20having%20a%20pretty%20good%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20I%20reached%2063%2C%20people%20would%20walk%20behind%20me%20on%20the%20street%2C%20walk%20past%2C%20and%20look%20back.%20There%20was%20no%20mistaking%20the%20look%20of%20surprise%20when%20they%20saw%20my%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2229878029-5356-4577-8316-71fabab6c4c7%5C%22%3EI%20looked%20after%20other%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECo-workers%20would%20often%20ask%20if%20I%20was%20OK%2C%20as%20if%20I%20seemed%20sad.%20I'd%20go%20into%20the%20bathroom%2C%20look%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%3F%20I%20do%20seem%20sad%20when%20I'm%20not%20smiling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20have%20cosmetic%20surgery%20in%20later%20life%3F%20Please%20email%20Jane%20Ridley%20at%20jridley%40insider.com%20if%20you'd%20like%20to%20share%20your%20experience.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20drooping%20marionette%20lines%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrandfather-blepharoplasty-surgery-to-be-more-confident-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eundereye%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20couldn't%20see%20my%20upper%20teeth%20because%20everything%20was%20sagging.%20They%20made%20me%20look%20like%20I%20was%20ready%20to%20cry%20any%20moment%2C%20though%20I%20wasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20in%202022%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20Max%2C%20died%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiagnosed-with-brain-cancer-at-25-how-i-stay-resilient-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrain%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20mourning%20for%20two%20years%2C%20but%20kept%20myself%20busy%20doing%20stuff%20on%20the%20house%20and%20helping%20with%20my%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20yellow%20dress%20holding%20a%20baby%20boy.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a02386ce1443b8dc48e400b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERandoph%20with%20her%20youngest%20grandchild%20before%20she%20had%20surgery.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Carolyn%20Randolph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20remarked%20that%20I%20was%20always%20doing%20stuff%20for%20other%20people%2C%20not%20myself.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20are%20you%20going%20to%20do%20something%20for%20yourself%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20said.%20%26quot%3BEver%20since%20I%20was%2063%2C%20I've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacelift-in-mexico-plastic-surgery-abroad-medical-turism-cheaper-cost-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewanted%20a%20facelift%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20The%20problem%20was%20that%20I%20hadn't%20been%20able%20to%20afford%20it.%20But%20now%20that%20I'd%20gotten%20some%20money%20from%20Max's%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fis-life-insurance-a-good-investment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20life%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20reconsidered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20heck%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20thought.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20I%20should%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%20I%20had%20a%20few%20consultations%20in%20my%20home%20city%20of%20Louisville%2C%20but%20didn't%20think%20the%20surgeons%20were%20quite%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225247d984-929e-48b5-80b5-914531cc26ea%5C%22%3EI%20had%20a%20deep%20plane%20facial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202024%2C%20I%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doctortruesdale.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Carl%20Truesdale%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Los%20Angeles.%20We%20immediately%20clicked.%20By%20luck%2C%20he%20happened%20to%20have%20a%20cancellation%2C%20and%20I%20had%20surgery%20on%20December%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20forehead%20lift%2C%20a%20deep-plane%20facelift%2C%20a%20neck%20lift%2C%20upper%20and%20lower%20blepharoplasty%2C%20and%20a%20little%20fat%20injected%20at%20the%20bridge%20of%20my%20nose%2C%20where%20it%20had%20flattened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Truesdale%20reassured%20me%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20look%20artificial.%20He%20said%20he%20could%20take%2030%20years%20off%20me.%20It%20made%20me