uot%3BQuicksilver%26quot%3B%20by%20Callie%20Hart.%3Cp%3EHachette%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESaeris%20Fane%20is%20focused%20on%20two%20things%3A%20getting%20enough%20water%20so%20that%20she%20and%20her%20brother%20can%20survive%20the%20desert%20heat%20of%20Zilvaren%2C%20the%20unforgiving%20homeland%20they%20live%20in%2C%20and%20keeping%20her%20alchemist%20powers%20a%20secret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she's%20caught%20stealing%20from%20the%20Undying%20Queen%2C%20Saeris%20thinks%20her%20life%20is%20about%20to%20end.%20Instead%2C%20her%20powers%20inadvertently%20activate%20a%20gateway%20to%20the%20snow-covered%20land%20of%20Yvelia%2C%20and%20Kingfisher%2C%20an%20intimidating%20and%20gorgeous%20fae%2C%20brings%20her%20through%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20saved%20her%20life%2C%20but%20now%20Saeris%20is%20trapped%20in%20Yvelia%2C%20forced%20to%20use%20her%20alchemist%20powers%20to%20help%20Kingfisher%20after%20making%20a%20deal%20with%20him.%20Saeris%20can't%20stand%20Kingfisher%2C%20but%20as%20she%20learns%20the%20ways%20of%20Yvelia%2C%20she%20discovers%20there's%20more%20to%20him%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20place%20in%20his%20world%20%E2%80%94%20than%20she%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BQuicksilver%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20installment%20in%20Callie%20Hart's%20%26quot%3BFae%20%26amp%3B%20Alchemy%26quot%3B%20series%2C%20has%20the%20same%20drama%20and%20magical%20fun%20as%20%26quot%3BACOTAR.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%26quot%3BBride%26quot%3B%20by%20Ali%20Hazelwood%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cover%20of%20%26quot%3BBride%26quot%3B%20by%20Ali%20Hazelwood.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a022fdfe1443b8dc48e3f8b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BBride%26quot%3B%20by%20Ali%20Hazelwood.%3Cp%3EPenguin%20Random%20House%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20your%20romantasy%20with%20a%20sp