sinessinsider.com%20(Samantha%20Grindell%20Pettyjohn)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22OpenAI%20made%20it%20harder%20to%20fire%20Sam%20Altman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223902%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sam%20Altman%20and%20Greg%20Brockman%20in%20court%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a021c33ba7ef34b41f3710e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222607%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman%20and%20Greg%20Brockman%20in%20court%3Cp%3EManuel%20Orbegozo%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20quietly%20changed%20its%20bylaws%20last%20year%2C%20said%20Elon%20Musk's%20expert%20witness%20in%20new%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20would%20only%20need%20one-third%20of%20the%20board's%20support%20to%20remain%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI's%20%26quot%3Bsupermajority%26quot%3B%20rules%20contrast%20with%20the%20trend%20of%20most%20large%20US%20public%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20board%20directors%20does%20it%20take%20to%20fire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-witness-testimony-hits-sam-altman-in-trial-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20More%20than%20was%20required%20in%202023%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20expert%20witness%20writes%20in%20new%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20OpenAI's%202025%20for-profit%20transition%2C%20it%20changed%20its%20governance%20structure%20to%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20fire%20the%20CEO%2C%20according%20to%20the%20documents%20released%20by%20the%20executive's%20lawyers%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBylaws%20adopted%20by%20OpenAI%20in%20October%202025%20allow%20the%20CEO%20to%20remain%20at%20the%20helm%20so%20long%20as%20he%20or%20she%20has%20at%20least%20one-third%20support%20from%20the%20for-profit%20entity's%20board%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20of%20the%20bylaws%20by%20Musk's%20expert%20witness%20conducted%20in%20November%202025%2C%20the%20documents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20new%20Bylaws%2C%20a%20%E2%85%94%20supermajority%20of%20the%20PBC's%20nonemployee%20directors%20is%20now%20needed%20to%20fire%20the%20CEO%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20excerpt%20of%20the%20analysis%20by%20Columbia%20law%20professor%20David%20M.%20Schizer%2C%20who%20took%20the%20witness%20stand%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20OpenAI's%20previous%20structure%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20board%20required%20a%20simple%20majority%2C%20or%20over%2050%25%2C%20to%20agree%20to%20remove%20the%20CEO%2C%20Schizer%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20structure%20emerges%20as%20Altman%20prepares%20to%20take%20the%20stand%20to%20defend%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-sam-altman-elon-musk-leadership-complaints-opneai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk's%20allegation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20and%20other%20OpenAI%20cofounders%20improperly%20converted%20OpenAI%20to%20a%20for-profit%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20has%20unearthed%20testimony%20from%20a%20range%20of%20executives%20and%20directors%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-sam-altman-did-so-bad-he-got-fired-openai-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAltman's%20surprise%202023%20firing%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20period%20employees%20now%20refer%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20blip%26quot%3B%20because%20he%20was%20quickly%20reinstated%20within%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eboard%20members%20told%20jurors%20last%20week%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-witness-testimony-hits-sam-altman-in-trial-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey%20fired%20Altman%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20part%20because%20they%20were%20concerned%20he%20was%20pushing%20products%20out%C2%A0without%20their%20knowledge%20and%20bypassing%20the%20nonprofit's%20AI%20safety%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20claims%20he%20donated%20%2438%20million%20to%20the%20original%20nonprofit%20entity%20because%20of%20false%20promises%20that%20it%20would%20remain%20an%20organization%20dedicated%20to%20developing%20AI%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20humanity%2C%20not%20for%20personal%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202023%2C%20four%20out%20of%20six%20board%20members%20agreed%20to%20the%20leadership%20change%2C%20citing%20his%20lack%20of%20candor%20in%20his%20communications%20with%20them%20over%20things%20like%20the%20release%20of%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20%26quot%3Bsupermajority%26quot%3B%20structure%2C%20Altman%20would%20only%20need%20two%20directors%20besides%20himself%20to%20remain%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20currently%20has%20eight%20directors%2C%20but%20only%20seven%20have%20voting%20power.%20So%20even%20if%20four%20of%20the%20current%20seven%20voting%20directors%20voted%20to%20remove%20him%2C%20they%20could%20not.%20The%20company's%20current%20roster%20of%20directors%20includes%20former%20co-CEO%20of%20Salesforce%2C%20Bret%20Taylor%3B%20Quora%20CEO%20Adam%20D'Angelo%3B%20Dr.%20Sue%20Desmond-Hellmann%3B%20and%20Altman%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernance%20organizations%20generally%20view%20simple%20majority%20voting%20as%20the%20standard%20for%20ensuring%20board%20accountability.%20Supermajority%20voting%20requirements%20are%20often%20criticized%20as%20tools%20of%20entrenchment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202024%2C%20proxy%20voting%20company%20ISS%20wrote%20that%20shareholder%20proposals%20to%20eliminate%20supermajority%20vote%20requirements%20were%20soaring%20among%20the%20biggest%20publicly%20traded%20US%20companies.%20ISS%20also%20said%20at%20the%20time%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20companies%20employing%20supermajority%20rules%20had%20declined%20to%20just%20over%20one-third.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20OpenAI%20would%20be%20in%20the%20minority%20if%20it%20were%20to%20start%20trading%20on%20public%20markets.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-trial-greg-brockman-testimony-elon-musk-breakup-compute-costs-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20executive%20Greg%20Brockman%3C%2Fa%3E%20confirmed%20last%20week%20that%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreg-brockman-openai-president-elon-musk-trial-testimony-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexploring%20an%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgreg-brockman-openai-president-elon-musk-trial-testimony-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-supermajority-majority-vote-fire-the-ceo-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778532024000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a021b8ae1443b8dc48e3ebd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-sam-altman-supermajority-majority-vote-fire-the-ceo-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22How%20many%20directors%20does%20it%20take%20to%20fire%20OpenAI's%20CEO%3F%20The%20bar%20has%20gotten%20higher%20since%20Sam%20Altman%20was%20sacked%20back%20in%202023%2C%20new%20court%20documents%20show.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kwhitehouse%40insider.com%20(Kaja%20Whitehouse)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trisha%E2%80%99s%20blue%20saree%20at%20Vijay%E2%80%99s%20swearing-in%20reminds%20fans%20of%20Aishwarya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778531869000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphot