3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rows%20of%20seats%20on%20a%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639ca8aab67d300019e7e338%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20air%20in%20plane%20cabins%20is%20very%20dry%2C%20so%20drink%20water%20and%20moisturize.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Hawk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20nothing%20like%20settling%20in%20for%20a%20long%20flight%20by%20kicking%20off%20your%20shoes%20and%20pulling%20on%20a%20comfy%20pair%20of%20socks%2C%20an%20amenity%20that%20crew%20members%20often%20hand%20out%20in%20first%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20you're%20supposed%20to%20wear%20those%20socks%20when%20you're%20sitting%20down%20in%20your%20seat%2C%20not%20when%20you're%20walking%20around%20the%20cabin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20many%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairplanes-are-as-dirty-as-you-might-think-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairplane%20carpets%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0weren't%20deep-cleaned%20very%20often.%20Because%20the%20cabin%20can%20get%20bumpy%20during%20turbulence%2C%20the%20liquid%20on%20the%20lavatory%20floor%20might%20also%20not%20be%20water.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20walk%20around%20without%20shoes%20on%2C%20pack%20some%20slippers%20to%20avoid%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20forget%20to%20test%20out%20their%20bulky%20neck%20pillows%20before%20packing%20them%20for%20a%20flight.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Suitcase%20with%20neck%20pillow%20on%20it%20next%20to%20person%20sitting%20in%20airport%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a023805c9dd4cb81cda94e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlways%20try%20out%20your%20pillow%20before%20carrying%20it%20onto%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3ETamina%208%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20swear%20by%20those%20classic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-travel-pillow%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EU-shaped%20neck%20pillows%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20daughter%20actually%20loves%20hers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20though%2C%20I've%20seen%20passengers%20schlep%20them%20all%20over%20the%20world%20only%20to%20hang%20them%20up%20on%20the%20plane%20after%20finding%20them%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20you%20burden%20yourself%20with%20such%20a%20bulky%20addition%20to%20your%20carry-on%2C%20test%20the%20pillow%20at%20home%20to%20make%20sure%20it's%20a%20good%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBe%20careful%20experimenting%20with%20sleep%20aids%20while%20in%20the%20air.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224554%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pills%20spilling%20out%20of%20prescription%20bottle%20-%20stock%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a0bef9b5600000185b5d98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223415%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPills%20spilling%20out%20of%20prescription%20bottle%20-%20stock%20photo%3Cp%3ETetra%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20assume%20you%20can%20wash%20down%20a%20sleep%20aid%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20drinks%20and%20stay%20comfortably%20asleep%20for%20precisely%20the%20right%20amount%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ftreatments%2Fare-sleeping-pills-safe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esleeping%20pills%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20lead%20to%20grogginess%20and%20other%20side%20effects%2C%20and%20you%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20be%20awake%20and%20alert%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20mechanical%20issue%20or%20other%20emergencies%20on%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20hard%20t