usinessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-fight-jet-lag-flight-attendants-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexperience%20jet%20lag%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20next%20day.%20This%20sort%20of%20logic%20applies%20to%20adults%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMany%20travelers%20don't%20drink%20enough%20water%20and%20arrive%20at%20their%20destinations%20dehydrated.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20fills%20up%20their%20metal%20water%20bottle.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F627290fff6bd4b0019cb5975%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22937%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20person%20fills%20up%20their%20reusable%20water%20bottle%20at%20an%20airport.%3Cp%3Emyboys.me%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20captain%20is%20constantly%20switching%20the%20seatbelt%20sign%20on%20and%20off%2C%20or%20you%20have%20to%20climb%20over%20other%20people%20to%20get%20to%20the%20lavatory%2C%20it%20can%20be%20tempting%20to%20ration%20your%20water%20intake%20on%20flights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20dry%20air%20and%20high%20altitude%20can%20both%20contribute%20to%20dehydration%2C%20which%20can%20then%20exacerbate%20jet-lag%20symptoms%20or%20lead%20to%20other%20health%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-flight-attendants-want-you-to-stop-doing-on-flight-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFlight%20attendants%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20frequently%20sweep%20through%20the%20cabin%20offering%20water%2C%20but%20if%20they%20don't%2C%20don't%20hesitate%20to%20ask%20for%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20have%20more%20control%20over%20the%20situation%2C%20consider%20bringing%20your%20own%20empty%20water%20bottle%20to%20fill%20after%20you%20pass%20through%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIf%20you're%20not%20wearing%20proper%20layers%2C%20you%20could%20end%20up%20uncomfortably%20hot%20or%20cold%20on%20the%20plane.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225557%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20plane.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a0bf2bb5600000185b5dac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224159%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20plane.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20hard%20to%20please%20everyone%2C%20and%20that's%20especially%20true%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20temperature%20inside%20an%20airplane%20that's%20hurtling%20across%20the%20world%20thousands%20of%20feet%20above%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20high%20probability%20that%2C%20at%20some%20point%2C%20the%20cabin%20will%20be%20too%20hot%20or%20too%20cold%20for%20your%20liking.%20You%20can%20try%20asking%20a%20flight%20attendant%20to%20tweak%20the%20temperature%2C%20but%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20another%20passenger%20may%20have%20just%20requested%20a%20change%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlay%20it%20safe%20by%20dressing%20in%20layers%20that%20are%20easy%20to%20pile%20on%20or%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDon't%20skip%20a%20chance%20to%20charge%20your%20devices.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22plane%20outlet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a0c10eb5600000185b5e7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEven%20if%20there%20are%20outlets%20on%20planes%2C%20they're%20not%20guaranteed%20to%20work.%3Cp%3EShutterStockStudio%3B%20Shutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20smart%20to%20load%20your%20devices%20up%20with%20movies%2C%20shows%2C%20and%20e-books%20before%20a%20long%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20make%20sure%20to%20keep%20your%20devices%20fully%20charged%20before%20you%20board%20because%20it's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20the%20outlets%20in%20a%20seat%2C%20a%20row%2C%20or%20an%20entire%20plane%20to%20stop%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20extra%20safe%2C%20bring%20a%20book%20or%20download%20a%20few%20podcasts%2C%20which%20won't%20drain%20your%20battery%20and%20will%20help%20you%20stay%20entertained%20through%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETravelers%20shouldn't%20rely%20on%20in-flight%20entertainment%2C%20which%20also%20doesn't%20always%20work.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screen%20on%20airplane%20tv%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639ca8bbb5600000185b1308%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20entertainment%20options%20on%20international%20flights.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Hawk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-survive-long-haul-flights-in-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong-haul%20flight%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20perfect%20opportunity%20to%20catch%20a%20new%20movie%20release%20or%20a%20TV%20series%20that%20streams%20on%20a%20channel%20you're%20not%20subscribed%20to%20at%20home.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20seat-back%20TVs%20can%20be%20finicky%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20chance%20the%20one%20in%20front%20of%20you%20won't%20work.%20If%20you're%20not%20the%20kind%20of%20person%20who%20can%20sleep%20all%20night%20on%20a%20plane%2C%20bring%20your%20own%20entertainment%20just%20in%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDrinking%20too%20much%20alcohol%20before%20or%20during%20a%20flight%20can%20worsen%20your%20experience.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22two%20drinks%20on%20airplane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F639cab62b5600000185b145b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPassengers%20should%20pace%20themselves%20with%20alcoholic%20beverages%20and%20drink%20plenty%20of%20water.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Hawk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20decreased%20blood-oxygen%20levels%20from%20low%20cabin%20pressure%20and%20dehydration%20from%20low%20humidity%2C%20alcohol's%20effects%20can%20feel%20like%20they%20hit%20much%20harder%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20inebriated%20passengers%20embarrass%20themselves%2C%20start%20fights%2C%20and%20vomit%20after%20boasting%20about%20how%20much%20alcohol%20they%20can%20handle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20saying%20you%20can't%20have%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20with%20dinner%20%E2%80%94%20I%20rarely%20pass%20up%20the%20opportunity%20%E2%80%94%20but%20please%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20misbehave%2C%20too%20much%20alcohol%20and%20dehydration%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20brutal%20case%20of%20jet%20lag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20forget%20small%20items%2C%20such%20as%20earplugs%20and%20moisturizers%2C%20that%20can%20make%20a%20flight%20way%20more%20comfortable.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20of%20a%20long%20distance%20new%20airplane%20with%20passengers%20sitting%20and%20resting%20during%20a%20long%20flight%20with%20picture%20taken%20from%20the%20back%20of%20the%20airplane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a0bf62b5600000185b5dbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EArtur%20Debat%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-its-like-flying-long-flight-in-world-business-class-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20cabin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20flight%20attendant%20may%20hand%20you%20a%20cute%20amenity%20kit.%20If%20you're%20in%20the%20back%2C%20though%2C%20you'll%20probably%20have%20to%20bring%20your%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20air%20in%20plane%20cabins%20tends%20to%20be%20low%20in%20moisture%2C%20so%20bring%20lip%20balm%20to%20keep%20your%20lips%20from%20chapping%20and%20lotion%20to%20keep%20your%20skin%20from%20flaking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20don't%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-airpods-anc-noise-canceling-scared-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enoise-canceling%20headphones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bring%20earplugs%20to%20block%20out%20the%20sound%20of%20people%20chewing%2C%20chattering%2C%20coughing%2C%20and%20pacing%20up%20and%20down%20the%20aisles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20eye%20mask%20can%20help%20shield%20your%20eyes%20from%20flashing%20TV%20screens%2C%20flight%20attendants'%20flashlights%2C%20and%20light%20streaming%20in%20from%20open%20window%20shades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20after%20a%20long%20night%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-best-and-worst-foods-to-eat-on-a-plane-2016-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeating%20airplane%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sipping%20wine%20and%20then%20waking%20up%20to%20breakfast%20and%20coffee%2C%20you'll%20probably%20appreciate%20having%20travel-size%20toothpaste%20and%20a%20toothbrush.%20At%20the%20very%20least%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20bring%20a%20stick%20of%20gum%20to%20freshen%20up%20your%20breath.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EYou%20may%20want%20to%20skip%20gassy%20foods%20and%20carbonated%20beverages%20when%20flying.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22international%20plane%20meal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63a1dc07d7277f00193f743d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22609%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20no%20guarantee%20that%20you'll%20love%20the%20in-flight%20menu%2C%20so%20bring%20snacks%20just%20in%20case.%3Cp%3ETiffany%20Hawk%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20airplane%20food%20is%20very%20processed%2C%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20that%20travelers%20want%20to%20fill%20up%20on%20salads%20and%20fresh%20vegetables%20at%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20do%20your%20best%20to%20lay%20off%20anything%20that%20can%20give%20you%20gas%2C%20including%20carbonated%20beverages.%20The%20low%20air%20pressure%20at%20cruise%20altitude%20causes%20gases%20to%20expand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20reason%20your%20bag%20of%20chips%20inflates%20like%20a%20balloon%2C%20and%20it%20explains%20why%20you%20may%20have%20to%20loosen%20your%20belt%20to%20accommodate%20your%20in-flight%20bloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20that%20trapped%20wind%20can%20be%20agonizing%2C%20which%20is%20why%20my%20airline%20trained%20its%20flight%20attendants%20to%20put%20passengers%20in%20flatulence-friendly%20positions%20to%20ease%20their%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20December%2019%2C%202022%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20updated%20on%20May%2011%2C%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-flight-worst-things-to-do-mistakes-flight-attendant-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778531805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a023d38c9dd4cb81cda951e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-flight-worst-things-to-do-mistakes-flight-attendant-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20flight%20attendant%2C%20there%20are%20mistakes%20I%20think%20you%20should%20avoid%20on%20a%20long%20international%20flight%20if%20you%20want%20to%20avoid%20jet%20lag%20and%20be%20comfortable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tiffany%20Hawk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Madhya%20Pradesh%20Youth%20Arrested%20For%20Killing%20Man%20Over%20Online%20Gaming%20Dispute%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20officer%2C%20Ramzan%20had%20allegedly%20lost%20around%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Sameer%20in%20online%20games%20and%20had%20repaid%20Rs%207%20lakh.%20However%2C%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20remaini