Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20writer%20and%20her%20boyfriend%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20glacier%20on%20a%20boat.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab0bb7d3e2f1aef36a22ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221190%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20some%20challenges%2C%20I%20feel%20lucky%20to%20explore%20the%20world%20with%20my%20favorite%20person.%3Cp%3EHaley%20Young%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20us%2C%20the%20greatest%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flive-with-couple-afford-rent-new-york-city-pros-cons-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20a%20small%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20finding%20ourselves%20at%20each%20other's%20throats%2C%20but%20becoming%20codependent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20constant%20travel%20means%20we%20don't%20see%20family%20and%20friends%20as%20regularly%20as%20we'd%20like%2C%20we%20can%20sometimes%20go%20weeks%20acting%20as%20load-bearing%20support%20in%20each%20other's%20social%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20usually%20feel%20like%20a%20problem%2C%20though.%20Most%20of%20all%2C%20I%20feel%20lucky%20to%20spend%20all%20day%2C%20every%20day%20with%20my%20favorite%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20March%2012%2C%202026%2C%20and%20most%20recently%20updated%20on%20May%2011%2C%202026.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvan-life-with-partner-helps-relationship-benefits-challenges-small-space-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778531283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69ab084f1fb3fcb426491015%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvan-life-with-partner-helps-relationship-benefits-challenges-small-space-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Living%20in%20a%20van%20for%20over%20