C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarines%20with%20the%2024th%20MEU%20train%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20quelling%20protests%20at%20US%20embassies%20when%20they%20deploy%2C%20at%20Camp%20Lejeune%2C%20North%20Carolina.%3Cp%3ELance%20Cpl.%20Payton%20Walley%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20any%20given%20time%2C%20Marines%20are%20preparing%20for%20the%20deployment%20of%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-netflix-documentary-marines-in-japan-training-for-conflict-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarine%20Expeditionary%20Units%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20robust%20naval%20crisis%20response%20force%2C%20said%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20senior%20adviser%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20and%20retired%20Marine%20colonel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20such%20MEUs%20are%20currently%20deployed%2C%20and%20combatant%20commanders%20want%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20won't%20say%20how%20many%20of%20the%20ARG-MEUs%20our%20combat%20commanders%20asked%20for%2C%20but%20it%20is%20well%20north%20of%20three%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Marine%20Corps%20commandant%2C%20Gen.%20Eric%20Smith%2C%20during%20remarks%20at%20the%20recent%20symposium%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-modern-warfare-expo-modern-day-marine-was-all-about-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmphibious%20Ready%20Groups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20warship%20groups%20carrying%20Marines.%20It's%20%26quot%3Blike%20double%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Navy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-clear-quick-shipbuilding-answer-to-navys-shrinking-fleet-report-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elacks%20the%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20such%20a%20request%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20but%20it's%20also%20unclear%20whether%20the%20Marines%20can%20meet%20such%20a%20demand%20consistently.%20Having%20three%20MEUs%20deployed%20at%20once%20is%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20unusual%2C%26quot%3B%20Cancian%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20in%20an%20unusually%20demanding%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20pay%20close%20attention%20to%20unit%20life%20cycles%20and%20have%20adult%20conversations%20about%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%2C%20the%202nd%20Marine%20Division%20commander%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20take%20our%20foot%20off%20the%20gas%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20modernization%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20have%20to%20look%20deep%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20drop%20any%20glass%20balls%20and%20put%20Marines%20in%20a%20position%20where%20we're%20deploying%20them%20and%20they're%20not%20ready%20to%20meet%20the%20mission%20that%20they%20have%20been%20tasked%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20putting%20Marines%20in%20the%20field%20with%20insufficient%20training%20and%20unfamiliar%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBringing%20infantry%2C%20artillery%2C%20mortars%2C%20and%20other%20capabilities%20together%20safely%20and%20effectively%20into%20what%20the%20US%20military%20calls%20%26quot%3Bcombined%20arms%26quot%3B%20requires%20extensive%2C%20coordinated%20training%2C%20and%20integrating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanduril-palmer-luckey-ai-war-conflict-defense-tech-startups-military-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enewer%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20drones%20and%20emerging%20technology%2C%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20complexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20where%20the%20tension%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224721%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marines%20with%20the%2022nd%20MEU%20practice%20fast%20roping%20from%20a%20Navy%20MH-60S%20Sea%20Hawk%20helicopter%20while%20on%20the%20amphibious%20assault%20ship%20USS%20Iwo%20Jima%20in%20the%20Caribbean%20Sea%2C%20April%202