dients%20for%20Garten's%20lemon%20pasta.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300534af8d001859a08a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten's%20lemon%20pasta%20dish%20includes%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECapellini%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUnsalted%20butter%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELemon%20(juice%20and%20zest)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that's%20really%20all%20there%20is%20to%20it!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20should%20note%20that%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20capellini%20at%20my%20local%20grocery%20store%20when%20I%20shopped%20for%20this%20recipe.%20A%20quick%20Google%20search%20informed%20me%20that%20thin%20spaghetti%20was%20a%20perfectly%20acceptable%20alternative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20we%20got%20cooking%2C%20I%20put%20a%20pot%20of%20salted%20water%20on%20the%20stove%20to%20boil%20and%20zested%20my%20two%20lemons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300535c46f0018c0b5e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20lot%20of%20lemon%20zest%2C%20but%20you%20really%20want%20a%20lot%20of%20flavor%2C%26quot%3B%20Garten%20says%20while%20making%20the%20dish%20on%20her%20show.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20zesting%20took%20a%20minute%20or%20two%2C%20and%20I%20was%20already%20halfway%20through%20all%20my%20prep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20it%20was%20time%20to%20juice%20the%20lemons.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300735c46f0018c0b5e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Garten%2C%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20cool%20electric%20juicer%2C%20let%20alone%20a%20handheld%20one!%20But%20a%20fork%20works%20fine%20for%20this%20task%20(and%20gives%20you%20a%20free%20arm%20workout).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20also%20noted%20that%20it's%20very%20important%20to%20use%20freshly%20squeezed%20juice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20definitely%20want%20to%20use%20fresh%20lemon%20juice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20juice%20lemons%20in%20advance%2C%20like%20a%20day%20or%20two%2C%20and%20leave%20them%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20it%20just%20isn't%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt%20was%20time%20to%20get%20cooking.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300c34af8d001859a08c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20threw%20my%20thin%20spaghetti%20into%20the%20pot%20of%20boiling%20water%2C%20albeit%20not%20very%20gracefully.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you%20go%20with%20capellini%20or%20thin%20spaghetti%2C%20make%20sure%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20your%20pasta%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20clock.%20These%20noodles%20cook%20much%20faster%20than%20most%20varieties%2C%20and%20Garten%20said%20they%20should%20be%20%26quot%3Bjust%20al%20dente%26quot%3B%20before%20you%20mix%20them%20in%20the%20sauce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20the%20noodles%20began%20to%20cook%2C%20I%20got%20started%20on%20my%20sauce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300934af8d001859a08b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten's%20recipe%20calls%20for%20two%20sticks%20of%20butter%2C%20which%20amounts%20to%20half%20a%20pound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%2C%20I%20know%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20butter%2C%26quot%3B%20Garten%20says%20on%20her%20show.%20%26quot%3BBut%20after%20a%20bad%20day%20at%20work%2C%20it's%20always%20good.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20a%20pound%20of%20butter%20still%20sounded%20a%20little%20overwhelming%2C%20especially%20on%20a%20night%20when%20I%20was%20also%20cooking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchrissy-teigens-steak-recipe-how-to-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChrissy%20Teigen's%20steak%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20myself%20and%20my%20friends.%20And%20when%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20comments%20for%20Garten's%20recipe%20on%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodnetwork.com%2Frecipes%2Fina-garten%2Flemon-capellini-3742575%23reviewsTop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20Network's%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20many%20readers%20had%20felt%20the%20same%20and%20cut%20the%20butter%20in%20half.%20So%20I%20followed%20suit%2C%20only%20adding%20one%20stick%20to%20my%20pan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%20I%20added%20the%20lemon%20juice%20and%20zest.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300d35c46f0018c0b5e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20added%20two%20teaspoons%20of%20salt%20and%20one%20teaspoon%20of%20pepper%20to%20the%20sauce%2C%20per%20Garten's%20instructions%2C%20and%20swirled%20the%20pan%20to%20mix%20everything%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20the%20pasta%20was%20ready%2C%20it%20was%20time%20to%20add%20it%20to%20the%20sauce.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300c35c46f0018c0b5e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20throws%20her%20pasta%20right%20in%20the%20sauce%2C%20using%20tongs%20to%20transfer%20the%20noodles%20to%20the%20pan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20copied%20her%2C%20letting%20the%20pasta%20sit%20in%20the%20sauce%20for%20a%20minute%20so%20that%20it%20could%20absorb%20all%20that%20butter%20and%20lemon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPer%20Garten's%20instructions%2C%20I%20also%20added%20some%20pasta%20water%20to%20the%20sauce%20to%20help%20keep%20my%20noodles%20moist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETen%20minutes%20hadn't%20even%20gone%20by%2C%20and%20the%20pasta%20was%20already%20ready.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60918a25f22c6b00185db99e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221228%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten%20recommends%20serving%20her%20lemon%20pasta%20with%20a%20little%20more%20lemon%20zest%20and%20juice%20on%20top%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20salt%20and%20pepper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%20Zach%20%E2%80%94%20who%20acted%20as%20my%20sous%20chef%20for%20the%20night%20%E2%80%94%20also%20had%20some%20fresh%20dill%20growing%20in%20his%20garden%2C%20so%20we%20added%20that%20on%20top%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGarten's%20lemon%20pasta%20is%20simple%20and%20fresh%2C%20but%20it%20works%20better%20as%20a%20side%20dish%20than%20the%20main%20event.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ina%20Garten%20Lemon%20Pasta%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F608b300c34af8d001859a08d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGarten's%20pasta%20has%20a%20lovely%20brightness%20to%20it%20that%20makes%20it%20perfect%20for%20spring%2C%20but%20there's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20depth%20in%20its%20flavor.%20My%20friends%20who%20helped%20me%20test%20the%20recipe%20that%20night%20also%20agreed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20totally%20get%20the%20appeal%20if%20it's%20so%20quick%20and%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Sara%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20a%20more%20satisfying%20meal%2C%20if%20that's%20the%20only%20dish%2C%20it%20could%20use%20one%20more%20element.%20Like%20adding%20shrimp%2C%20for%20me%20personally%2C%20would%20make%20it%20complete.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pasta%20was%20super%20yummy%20and%20had%20me%20mad%20at%20myself%20for%20every%20time%20I've%20bought%20a%20%2420%20pasta%20limon%20from%20a%20restaurant%20when%20it's%20so%20simple%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20Tyler%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20great%20alongside%20the%20steak%2C%20but%20if%20we%20were%20just%20having%20the%20pasta%20on%20its%20own%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20a%20little%20disappointed%20because%20it%20wasn't%20anything%20too%20special.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20Garten's%20pasta%20would%20be%20a%20great%20side%20at%20a%20dinner%20party%2C%20or%20a%20quick%20weeknight%20dinner%20with%20some%20protein%20or%20veggies%20mixed%20in.%20And%20serving%20it%20alongside%20Garten's%20delicious%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthis-is-how-to-make-ina-gartens-garlic-bread-recipe-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egarlic%